thread.title_full: Auto Europe Canada reviewed by Frank

author: Frank
title: Frank
text: The booking procedure was fast. Car choices sand the costs presented, pick up places as well as opening hours (very important) mentioned. But prices and rebates of different car rental comp. should be checked too and can be s.t. cheaper. Depends on weekdays and hours of your booking. The rental itself and the transfer at the office will tell us if AU has a positive influence on the quality of rental service of companies it represents.
